\check Analyze Zero-Width Characters
\submenu Indic
\script AnalyzeZeroWidthCharacters.py
\description Analyzes occurrences of ZWJ and ZWNJ characters in the text, based on a wordlist that you have exported from Paratext. Before running this tool, please export a wordlist, saving it in the project folder with the name WORDLIST.XML. This tool will create (overwriting if necessary) a file in the same folder called Standard_Clusters.TXT containing the most frequently-occurring form of each cluster. Before using this tool, please read the Help file for detailed instructions. [Version 0.3]
\toText
\helpFile AnalyzeZeroWidthCharacters.rtf
\utf8


